chunk: My journey with web-development started in Antwerp with a 7 month bootcamp provided by becode Antwerp
Their goal was to help motivated job seekers landing their first job as developers
Their methodology was based on teamwork with on-demand guidance, which was a perfect fit for me
We were mainly figuring things out on our own but also learned when to ask questions and how to formulate them.
In short it wasn’t only about learning specific things but mainly learning how to grow as developers
